data.description: Beautiful 4 Bedroom Home with Pool, Fresh Paint, and New Floors! Welcome home to this stunning 4 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom property that offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and relaxation. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is packed with features that will make everyday living a joy. Freshly Painted: The neutral color palette creates a bright and inviting atmosphere, ready for you to add your personal touch. Private Pool: Escape the summer heat and enjoy endless hours of fun and relaxation in your very own backyard. Spacious Bedrooms: With 4 generous bedrooms, there's plenty of room for the entire family. Each bedroom offers ample space, natural light, and closet storage, ensuring everyone has their own private sanctuary. The two bathrooms both have dual vanities and linen closets. Open Living Space: The home boasts a spacious layout, seamlessly connecting the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The natural flow of the floor plan creates an ideal space for gathering with family and friends, making entertaining a breeze.  Chef's Kitchen: The well-appointed kitchen features modern appliances, ample storage, granite countertops and a convenient work island. New Floors: The upgraded flooring not only enhances the aesthetic appeal but also provides durability and easy maintenance. Outdoor Living: Enjoy barbecues, gardening, or simply relaxing in your own private outdoor space on this fenced large lot. Convenient Location: Situated in a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping centers, and major transportation routes making life easier and convenient.  Recent Updates: flooring 2023, water heater 2022, HVAC 2020, saltwater pool conversion and new liner 2022. It's the perfect place to create lasting memories. Contact your favorite agent today to schedule a viewing and take the first step towards calling this wonderful property your new home!
